title: Ep 132: Old Navy Haul with Kelsey McKinney of "Normal Gossip"
itunes:title: Ep 132: Old Navy Haul with Kelsey McKinney of "Normal Gossip"
itunes:subtitle: Sorry about the 1-900 voice!
description:
Author of "God Spare The Girls" Kelsey McKinney is here to extol the virtues of the best Old Navy has to offer, as well as a kitchen sink accessory that makes dish doing easier. She's also the host of Normal Gossip, a podcast about great pieces of gossip, shared and retold anonymously for your entertainment. 


Old Navy Favs:

  • - Linen/Cotton Drawstring Pants
  • -Bodysuit 
  • -Ribbed Dress 
  • -Matching Athleisure Track Suit Set  

Dish Accessory:

  • -Umbra Dish Squeegee 



Shop our Amazon Storefront: https://www.amazon.com/shop/geethanksjustboughtit 

 

Gee Thanks! appreciates its supporters, especially Alley Peplinski, Becca Sheaffer, Allie Nagy, Angi James, Lindsay Creech and Erin Gibson! 

 

Want to support? Join the Patreon! Sign up: https://www.patreon.com/geethanksandfriends**
